{"type":"answer","id":117081,"parentType":"question","parentId":14314,"uid":2791,"contents":"大陆不断有<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/贫困县.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">贫困县</a>被揭耗巨资搞政绩工程。近期，贵州省“国家级贫困县”<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/独山县.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">独山县</a>县委书记<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/潘志立.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">潘志立</a>因受贿而被起诉，调查发现该县的负债高达400多亿元人民币。而该县耗巨资22亿元人民币，建造了一座山寨版“<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/gb/紫禁城.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">紫禁城</a>”，由潘志立负责该工程。<br>\n<br>\n不用等到民主啦，共匪造那么多面子工程早就欠债几十万亿了，看那地铁高铁个个在未来都是地雷哦。","date":"2019-12-30","agreeCount":5,"discussionCount":1}